examples.en: You need special authorization to park here.
He abandoned his post without authorization.
He has no authorization to act on our behalf.
Do you have authorization for this expenditure?
We received authorization to begin demolition.
His authorization to go ahead with the project was finally given.
Deputies are given authorization to make arrests.
You will need the authorization of the council before you can act.
Children may not leave the building without the authorization of the principal.
